page.title: 05TRANSPORT IN MYDDLE
page.content: Most of the {TRANSPORT }in {MYDDLE }is {LAUNCHBURY'S LORRIES LTD}. The company contains:Thirteen trucks. Seven D.A.F. trucks and six ordinary trucks,the colour of the trucks is { {MAROON. They Transport:Sugar Beet, Grain, Potatoes, Bricks and Boxes. They are staitioned at {HILLCREST {GARAGE}(Owned by {LAUNCHBURY'S LTD}.) The farthest they go is {LIVERPOOL. The company was formed in the late { {SIXTIES. The company's owner is {MR NEIL {LAUNCHBURY. There are about ten drivers of the trucks. The work force is about twenty. The trucks are all about twenty metres long.
